					<additions><p>F.1r: twelve or so seals some with notes (including among the seals: Luṭf Allāh, 1093; Luṭf Allāh, 1089; others are dated 1166 and 1197). Final folio: 2 identical seals dated 1197 also found on f.1r. The codex contains many diagrams and figures often finely drawn, but towards the end there are many spaces where diagrams were never inserted.</p> 
